videos.description: Seth Lundy knocks down the corner 3 to account for more than half of Penn State's points.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Lundy scores 11th straight point for Penn State) 2020/2/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lundy scores 11th straight point for Penn State

videos.description: Bakari Evelyn is left alone behind the arc and knocks down the wide-open 3-pointer to extend Iowa's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Evelyn left wide open for Iowa 3) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Evelyn left wide open for Iowa 3

videos.description: In the closing moments of the game, Iowa breaks Penn State's press and gets the ball to Luka Garza under the hoop for the dunk.
